<html>
<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
meditate : changes your character position to meditating<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
Meditate allows monks to relax their bodies and, through the grace of<br>
their gods, cure their wounds much quicker than normal.  Doing this<br>
requires magical energy though.  To stop meditating, simply stand.<br>
<br>
See also: trance<br>
</html>
</body>
